Search



























We're Building TheBuilding Industry

From foundation to ridge, our connector and software solutions will ensure your structure is optimized to be safe and code compliant.










Look for the MiTek® Name


You'll be seeing the MiTek brand appearing more predominately on our line of structural connectors,  hardware,  anchoring solutions, and other products. Look for MiTek at trade shows and on retail set signage at dealers and major retail locations across the country.











USP Product Catalog


The USP catalog is a comprehensive 236 page guide to over 3000 connector products featuring all new product and application illustrations
UPDATE! USP Catalog App now available for iPhone, iPad, Android and Windows Mobile Devices.
Free Download in US and Canadian versions on iTunes App Store, Google Play & Windows Store. Search for USP Catalog. Request a hard copy.






Product Feature: INCREDI-BOND® Multi-Purpose Epoxy


INCREDI-BOND® is a high strength two-component epoxy specifically designed to be a bonding agent for almost all household materials including wood, steel, concrete, brick, stone and CMU block. Learn about INCREDI-BOND and our full line of epoxy products for cracked and uncracked concrete, masonry, general purpose and DOT.











