USPSpecifier™


NEW Version 1.7Free project management and cost control software simplifies access to information on over 3000 structural connectors through an intuitive and graphical desktop interface. 








USPDeck Designer™


Free online interactive software program that will help you and your clients design the deck of their dreams. Easy to use, customize and collaborate. Powered by DIY Technologies.  A MiTek® Company.








USPAdhesive Anchor Design™


NEW Software - Download NowFree Adhesive Anchor Design software that provides optimized epoxy connection solutions for threaded anchors post-installed into concrete.










MiTek®SAPPHIRE™ Supply


Whole house design software tailored to the lumber dealers EWP design and estimating operations. Sapphire Supply is available exclusively to USP Stocking dealers. 








USPEpoxy Quantity Estimator


Do you need to know how much epoxy your job needs? Quickly calculate the number of cartridges using the USP Epoxy Quantity Estimator. Run our web application on your desktop, smart phone or tablet from anywhere with an internet connection.



     
  
















 
 









